loading="lazy"
>&lt;br>
然后就可以开始尽情的玩耍了&lt;br>
&lt;img src="http://localhost:1313/2.jpg"
loading="lazy"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 id="jupyter-notebook卸载">Jupyter notebook卸载
&lt;/h1>&lt;p>使用&lt;strong>pip uninstall jupyter&lt;/strong>是无法卸载的必须使用下面方法。&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">pip install pip-autoremove
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">pip-autoremove jupyter -y
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
